additionalProperty.value: Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner. Adults only. The recommended daily dose of this medicine contains 338mg of sodium. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. This product is suitable for consumption during Pregnancy and Breastfeeding. We recommend consulting your Primary Healthcare Professional when considering changes to your supplementary routine, particularly during Pregnancy and Breastfeeding, so that your situation can be monitored as necessary.
